```tactics
lemma sum_WickContraction_nil (f : WickContraction 0 → M) [AddCommMonoid M] :
    ∑ c, f c = f empty := by
  rw [Finset.sum_eq_single_of_mem]
  simp only [Finset.mem_univ]
  intro b hb
  fin_cases b
  simp
```

This lemma states that when summing a function `f` over `WickContraction 0`, the sum equals `f empty` because `WickContraction 0` has only one element.

